  "style": "APA",
  "texts": [
    "This approach risks overfitting to specific linguistic features rather than enabling robust generalization to diverse contexts (Serapio-García et al., 2023; Xu et al., 2024; Mizrahi et al., 2024).",
    "Role-based personality prompts can disproportionately shape LLM behavior, causing reasoning patterns to be overly narrow and limited to the explicit traits highlighted in the prompt (Zheng et al., 2023; Lu et al., 2021; Sclar et al., 2023).",
    "This influence may lead to imbalanced or overly constrained responses, especially in tasks requiring broader or more nuanced cognitive engagement.",
    "A more comprehensive discussion of the background and related work can be found in Appendix B and Appendix C.",
    "The lack of large-scale datasets featuring personality-grounded dialogues poses a significant challenge."
  ],
